author: pbs.org
title: Clinton and Sanders dominate policy-deep Democratic debate
text: The first Democratic debate between five presidential candidates sharpened into a two-person heavyweight match between between Bernie Sanders and Hillary Clinton over capitalism and gun control. Political director Lisa Desjardins reports.
